summary: This mod Adds a New Follower to the game
descriptionHtml:
This Mods A New Follower to The game.

You can Find Lady Violet Outside of labyrinthion. She is ja Summoner with an Unique Class. Immortal and you can Marri her.

She is A Breton so if use an other body she should work fine.


I Personly use CBBE with Fairskin and the Demonic skin ontop.
